title: A brief discussion on Monty Python and they're influence on comedy
itunes:title: A brief discussion on Monty Python and they're influence on comedy
description:
Guest Host Ian Punnett and David Morgan discuss the history of the comedy troupe Monty Python and how they changed Comedy. David tells a story about what happened when ABC bought six episodes to air on network television.
